#

Burrito Bowl

25 min
$10
600 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeVegetarian

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

QuickEasyHealthyCustomizable

Description

A delicious and customizable burrito bowl filled with rice, beans, fresh veggies, and your choice of protein.

Ingredients

  • cooked rice: 1 cup
  • black beans: 1/2 cup
  • corn: 1/2 cup
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • avocado: 1, diced
  • shredded cheese: 1/2 cup
  • sour cream: 1/4 cup
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
